public class ForceJDOPersistenceManagerFactory
extends org.datanucleus.jdo.JDOPersistenceManagerFactory

We don't support JDO. Use JPA instead. Factory for the JDOPersistenceManager. Overriding so we can provide our own PersistenceManager
